    <div class="bg-light-gray">
      <p>This is statically positioned content</p>
    </div>
    <h3 class="f3">Position Relative</h3>
    <div class="relative top-4 bg-black-20 bold pam">
      <p class="f3">This is relatively positioned content that doesn’t affect
        the position of other elements which is why the text overlaps with the
        content that is set to position static.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="static bg-black-10 gray">
      <p>
        This is also statically positioned content This is also statically
